responses through my hack.  Tonight I was in a silly mood, though,  and 
tried doing a little magic act with Oscar to have him read my mind.  I 
don&#39;t know if it was from being goofy or because of the full moon, but I 
got 3 responses from him in one little 2 minute recording.  I&#39;m assuming 
it&#39;s the former, since his responses were a little on the silly side, too.

